casebody.data:
Tuesday, August 26, 1997

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

95-2646. In re Resignation of Guth.

This matter is pending before this court upon the filing by respondent of a motion for continuance of the August 26,1997 hearing. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for continuance be granted for sixty days, and that the hearing be rescheduled for November 4,1997, at 9:00 a.m.
